2c72e3ba-a201-4ae6-80f2-a36044b8d52e.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same.
2c72e3ba-a201-4ae6-80f2-a36044b8d52e.see_description: In the input, you should see...light blue, dark blue and black boxes. The light blue boxes represent an incomplete rectangle.
